# 💳 Credit Card Fraud Detection

A machine learning pipeline for detecting fraudulent transactions on a 
highly imbalanced financial dataset — achieving 93–95% recall on the 
minority fraud class.

## 🔍 Overview
Financial fraud detection is a class-imbalance problem where missing a 
fraud case is far costlier than a false alarm. This project applies SMOTE 
oversampling and XGBoost to maximize fraud-class recall while maintaining 
overall precision — evaluated with ROC-AUC, F1, Precision, and Recall.

## ✨ Features
- Handles severe class imbalance (~0.17% fraud ratio)
- SMOTE oversampling for minority class augmentation
- Threshold tuning for precision-recall tradeoff
- Full evaluation suite: Confusion Matrix, ROC-AUC, F1

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
`Python` `Scikit-learn` `XGBoost` `SMOTE` `Pandas` `Matplotlib` `Seaborn`

## 📊 Results
| Metric | Score |
